_header: Lord God as Thou art all good

BLEge3245.First Lines: Lord god as þu art al goodAnd of myht he þat al may…
BLEge3245.Last Lines: …Strenkþe me a geyn temptaciunAnd saue me fro dampnaciun
BLEge3245.Note: Lines 11-12 written on a single line.
